Greene King Food-Driven Sales to Rise Further, CEO Tells Sky

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-04T19:48:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-04/greene-king-food-driven-sales-to-rise-further-ceo-tells-sky.html
Greene King Plc (GNK)  Chief Executive
Officer Rooney Anand told Sky News in an interview that sales of
food in the company’s pubs have doubled since 2007 and he thinks
the company could see “75 percent of retail business being
food-driven.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 